nodes.text: A clone trooper officer served as an unit commander in the Grand Army of the Republic during the Clone Wars between the Galactic Republic and the Confederacy of Independent Systems as part of the 41st Scout Battalion of the 41st Elite Corps. The officer ordered all units of Red Company to relocate, and later participated in the Battle of Kashyyyk towards the end of the war.
The clone trooper first appeared, albeit only by voice, in the 2005 film Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith. He was voiced by actor Temuera Morrison.
